    "translation":{"eng":"“Mukunda! Mādhava! Yādava! Hari! Everyone, chant! Everyone chant, filling your mouths with the holy names of the Lord! Oh, you pass your nights in vain, captivated by sleep, and your days in decorating your body. “Don’t any of you think about what you are doing, having achieved this rare human body? If you do not worship the son of Yaśodā now, you will fall into a shameful condition at the time of death."}},{
