    "translation":{"eng":"Drink the pure nectar of kṛṣṇa-nāma and thus give relief to Bhaktivinoda’s burning heart. There is nothing except the holy name within all the fourteen worlds. Desiring to benefit the living entities, these sweet holy names have come to the material world. They shine like the sun in the sky of the heart, destroying the darkness of ignorance."}}
